Body: Non-governmental organizations, community groups and government agencies and other disaster management stakeholders.
The offices of organizations, their addresses and contact details.
The resources such as tools and equipment available to organizations and neighborhoods to support disaster management activities.
The details and locations of projects carried out by organizations.
The staff working for organizations and information on their contact details and trainings.
The volunteers supporting organizations and information on their contact details and trainings.
The details and locations of camps providing shelter to people displaced by disasters and refugees, including registration of people in camps.
